OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FJames Murray MP, the Secretary of
OL,7,FState for Health and Social Care,
OL,8,Fconfirms Martha's Rule will be
OL,9,Fextended following the "devastating"
OL,10,FOckenden report. Watch the full
OL,11,Finterview with our Political
OL,12,FCorrespondent, Alison Mackenzie.
OL,14,FThe Health Secretary has told ITV News
OL,15,FCentral "nothing is off the table"
OL,16,Fwhen questioned about the possibility
OL,17,Fof a public inquiry into maternity
OL,18,Ffailings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FIt comes after a review found more
OL,7,Fthan 500 mothers and babies suffered
OL,8,Fpotentially avoidable harm or died due
OL,9,Fto "deeply embedded systemic failures"
OL,10,Fat the "toxic" Nottingham University
OL,11,FHospitals NHS Trust.
OL,13,FMothers and babies have been offered
OL,14,Ffurther protection as Martha's Rule,
OL,15,Fthe right to an urgent independent
OL,16,Freview, is rolled out to all maternity
OL,17,Fsettings on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FThe inquiry, led by senior midwife
OL,7,FDonna Ockenden, found leaders at
OL,8,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,9,FTrust (NUH) knew there were serious
OL,10,Fissues in its maternity department
OL,11,Fgoing back years, but failed to take
OL,12,Faction to prevent more deaths.
OL,14,FOverall, 520 mothers and babies
OL,15,Fsuffered potentially avoidable harm or
OL,16,Fdeath, including 94 babies who were
OL,17,Fstillborn.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FThe scheme was created after 13-year-
OL,7,Fold Martha Mills developed sepsis
OL,8,Fwhile under the care of King's College
OL,9,FHospital NHS Foundation Trust in south
OL,10,FLondon in 2021, with a coroner ruling
OL,11,Fshe would have survived if medics had
OL,12,Fpicked up on the warning signs of her
OL,13,Fcondition and transferred her to
OL,14,Fintensive care earlier.
OL,16,FThe Secretary of State for Health and
OL,17,FSocial Care, James Murray, told ITV
OL,18,FNews Central a public inquiry into
OL,19,Fmaternity failings is not "off the
OL,20,Ftable".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FHe said: "The report from Donna
OL,7,FOckenden is devastating, it's horrific
OL,8,Fto read.
OL,10,F"What really struck me is that the
OL,11,Ffamilies have been the driving force
OL,12,Fbehind this review happening. I don't
OL,13,Fthink we should take anything off the
OL,14,Ftable at this stage.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"When I've been talking to the
OL,7,Ffamilies, some of them want a public
OL,8,Finquiry, others take a different view,
OL,9,Fbut what unites all the families is a
OL,10,Fdesire for accountability and for
OL,11,Fchanges to happen, so that maternity
OL,12,Fservices are delivered so that women
OL,13,Fare listened to."
OL,15,FHe said the review laid bare "a
OL,16,Fculture where too many voices went
OL,17,Funheard, too many opportunities to
OL,18,Fprevent harm were missed and too many
OL,19,Flives were lost."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FMartha's Rule has been rolled out for
OL,7,Finpatients in every acute hospital in
OL,8,FEngland and has already been piloted
OL,9,Fin 15 maternity and neonatal settings,
OL,10,Fwith more rollouts expected this year.
OL,12,FThe government has also suggested they
OL,13,Fmay use the Public Office
OL,14,F(Accountability) Bill - also known as
OL,15,Fthe Hillsborough Law Bill - to compel
OL,16,FNHS staff - past and present - to give
OL,17,Fevidence or face up to two years in
OL,18,Fprison.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FWhile statutory inquiries have this
OL,7,Fpower, independent reviews do not. The
OL,8,FPublic Office (Accountability) Bill is
OL,9,Fcurrently going through Parliament.
OL,11,FIn a full statement, James Murray MP
OL,12,Fsaid: "Last week I met with the
OL,13,Ffamilies in Nottingham and heard first-
OL,14,Fhand about the devastating loss they
OL,15,Fhave suffered often caused by
OL,16,Fhorrendous care they received on the
OL,17,FNHS.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"Donna Ockenden's review lays bare a
OL,7,Fculture where too many voices went
OL,8,Funheard, too many opportunities to
OL,9,Fprevent harm were missed and too many
OL,10,Flives were lost. That's why we have to
OL,11,Ftake action, and quickly.
OL,13,F"No family should ever have to battle
OL,14,Fthe system that is meant to care and
OL,15,Fprotect them, that is why Martha's
OL,16,FRule is so fundamental.
OL,18,F"It provides a way for a concerned
OL,19,Fmum, or family member to raise the
OL,20,Falarm before it is too late.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"I want families across the country to
OL,7,Ffeel safe when they walk through the
OL,8,Fdoors of their maternity settings.
OL,9,FToday marks a step in achieving that -
OL,10,Fbut this is just the beginning.
OL,12,F"I want to thank Donna for her work
OL,13,Fover the last four years. These clear
OL,14,Frecommendations will form part of our
OL,15,Fnational plan to deliver real
OL,16,Fimprovements in maternal and neonatal
OL,17,Fcare, in Nottingham and beyond."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FDonna Ockenden said following the
OL,7,Freview: "To every family who came
OL,8,Fforward, I want to say this: we have
OL,9,Flistened.
OL,11,F"It is my sincere hope that through
OL,12,Fthis Review you now feel as though
OL,13,Fyour voices have been heard and what
OL,14,Fhappened to you and your families has
OL,15,Fbeen recognised and will be acted upon.
OL,26,@oD@IOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"Today, we have started the process of
OL,7,Fproviding answers. We have set out
OL,8,Fclear findings and essential actions
OL,9,Fto address the concerns raised by
OL,10,Ffamilies and staff. These actions when
OL,11,Fimplemented will drive improvement
OL,12,Fboth within perinatal services at
OL,13,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,14,FTrust and across England."
OL,26,@vD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"While the majority of births on the
OL,7,FNHS are safe, too many families have
OL,8,Fsuffered harm that should never have
OL,9,Fhappened. Their experiences will drive
OL,10,Freal and lasting change to maternity
OL,11,Fservices in England, driven by staff
OL,12,Fworking to improve services."
OL,14,F"We have listened": Chair of the
OL,15,FIndependent Review Donna Ockenden
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FDonna Ockenden, Chair of the
OL,7,FIndependent Review, said: "Today, the
OL,8,FIndependent Review into Maternity
OL,9,FServices at Nottingham University
OL,10,FHospitals NHS Trust has published its
OL,11,Ffindings, conclusions and actions.
OL,13,F"First and foremost, the Review Team
OL,14,Fand I would like to express our
OL,15,Fdeepest gratitude to the thousands of
OL,16,Ffamilies, staff and community
OL,17,Frepresentatives who placed their trust
OL,18,Fin us and contributed to this Review.
OL,26,@oD@[OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"Many shared the most painful chapters
OL,7,Fof their lives, speaking with
OL,8,Fextraordinary courage about
OL,9,Fexperiences of trauma and grief. They
OL,10,Fdid so not only in pursuit of answers
OL,11,Ffor themselves, but in the hope that
OL,12,Fno other family would have to endure
OL,13,Fwhat they have experienced.
OL,15,F"To every family who came forward, I
OL,16,Fwant to say this: we have listened. It
OL,17,Fis my sincere hope that through this
OL,18,FReview you now feel as though your
OL,19,Fvoices have been heard and what
OL,20,Fhappened to you and your families has
OL,21,Fbeen recognised and will be acted upon.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"This Review has been ongoing for more
OL,7,Fthan three years. For many families,
OL,8,Fhowever, the journey began long before
OL,9,Fthat. Some have carried the burden of
OL,10,Funanswered questions and compounded
OL,11,Fharm for more than a decade. We
OL,12,Frecognise the emotional toll that this
OL,13,Fprocess has taken on families and
OL,14,Fstaff alike.
OL,16,F"Today, we have started the process of
OL,17,Fproviding answers. We have set out
OL,18,Fclear findings and essential actions
OL,19,Fto address the concerns raised by
OL,20,Ffamilies and staff.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"These actions when implemented will
OL,7,Fdrive improvement both within
OL,8,Fperinatal services at Nottingham
OL,9,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust and
OL,10,Facross England.
OL,12,F"The evidence heard by the Review Team
OL,13,Fmakes clear that we are not yet
OL,14,Fconsistently providing safe, equitable
OL,15,Fand compassionate care to all women,
OL,16,Fbabies and families. That must change.
OL,18,F"The Trust faces a significant journey
OL,19,Fof improvement ahead. However, it is
OL,20,Fimportant to acknowledge that progress
OL,21,Fhas already begun."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FShe added, "To those who have feared
OL,7,Fthat this report might become another
OL,8,Fdocument on a shelf, I want to be
OL,9,Fclear: it will not. The findings
OL,10,Fpublished today must be the catalyst
OL,11,Ffor safer care, greater accountability
OL,12,Fand lasting improvement.
OL,14,F"The families of Nottinghamshire, the
OL,15,Fstaff of the Trust, and the wider
OL,16,Fcommunities it serves have my personal
OL,17,Fand unwavering commitment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G18/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"We owe it to those whose lives have
OL,7,Fbeen forever changed to ensure that
OL,8,Flessons are learned, improvements are
OL,9,Fdelivered, and that future families
OL,10,Freceive the safe and compassionate
OL,11,Fcare they deserve."
OL,13,F"We failed you": the bosses of
OL,14,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust
OL,15,Frespond
OL,26,@sD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G19/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34820
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FIn a statement responding to the
OL,7,Freview, the Nottingham University
OL,8,FHospital NHS Trust said, "Today,
OL,9,FWednesday 24 June, the findings from
OL,10,Fthe Independent Maternity Review (IMR)
OL,11,Finto services at Nottingham University
OL,12,FHospitals NHS Trust (NUH) were
OL,13,Fpublished.
OL,15,F"The Review, led by Donna Ockenden,
OL,16,Foutlines how, where and why care in
OL,17,Four services had resulted in harm to
OL,18,Fmothers and babies in their hospitals
OL,19,Fand made recommendations of actions to
OL,20,Fimprove care in the future.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G20/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34821
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"Wefullyaccept thefindings of the
OL,7,FReview andtake responsibility for the
OL,8,Ffailings that are detailed within it.
OL,9,FAn initial response to the review,
OL,10,Fshared by Chief Executive Anthony May
OL,11,Fand Trust Chair Nick Carver, follows.
OL,13,F"We will now take time to carefully
OL,14,Fconsider and reflect further on the
OL,15,FReview outcomes and its
OL,16,Frecommendations."
OL,18,FThey've also written an open letter to
OL,19,Fthe people of Nottinghamshire:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G21/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34822
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"The publication of the independent
OL,7,Freview into maternity services in
OL,8,FNottingham is a watershed moment for
OL,9,Faffected families, our staff and for
OL,10,Fthe communities we serve.
OL,12,F"We apologise unreservedly to the
OL,13,Fwomen and families who have suffered
OL,14,Fharm, loss, trauma or distress while
OL,15,Freceiving care in our services. We
OL,16,Ffailed you, and on behalf of
OL,17,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust,
OL,18,Fwe accept responsibility for our
OL,19,Ffailings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G22/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34823
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"Many families have been generous
OL,7,Fenough to meet with us, showing
OL,8,Fextraordinary courage and
OL,9,Fdetermination. We are grateful for
OL,10,Fthat, and we want you to know that the
OL,11,Fpublication of this report is not the
OL,12,Fend of a process. It is another
OL,13,Fimportant milestone in a journey that
OL,14,Fmust continue. Your bravery and
OL,15,Fcommitment to speaking up is helping
OL,16,Fimprove maternity care.
OL,18,F"We want to thank Donna Ockenden for
OL,19,Fher work and for engaging with us
OL,20,Fthroughout this process."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G23/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34824
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,FThe NHS Trust added, "We recognise
OL,7,Fthat trust is earned through actions,
OL,8,Fnot words. We know, also, that
OL,9,Ffamilies and the wider public will
OL,10,Fjudge us not by what we say today, but
OL,11,Fby what we do next.
OL,13,F"The review makes clear that while
OL,14,Fimprovements have been made, there is
OL,15,Fstill more to do. We will take time to
OL,16,Freflect on the report with humility,
OL,17,Fhonesty and determination.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G24/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34825
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"At the same time, we will work with
OL,7,Ffamilies on a meaningful apology
OL,8,Fbecause we know it is important to
OL,9,Fthem that this is reflective of the
OL,10,Ffindings of the review, and our
OL,11,Fcommitment to lasting improvement. We
OL,12,Fcan say with certainty that families
OL,13,Fwill continue to be involved in our
OL,14,Fimprovement plans because this review
OL,15,Fhas proved that we can learn from them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G25/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34826
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782478095
OL,3,CHealth Secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry into maternity failings
OL,6,F"We must also acknowledge our staff.
OL,7,FEvery day we see dedicated,
OL,8,Fcompassionate professionals working
OL,9,Ftirelessly to provide the best
OL,10,Fpossible care for women and families,
OL,11,Foften under extreme pressure and
OL,12,Fscrutiny."
OL,14,FThe statement concluded, "On behalf of
OL,15,Fthe Trust, we renew the commitments to
OL,16,Ftransparency, openness and
OL,17,Faccountability. Most importantly, we
OL,18,Frenew our commitment to providing
OL,19,Fsafe, high-quality maternity care at
OL,20,Fyour hospitals."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G26/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
